Package: pop-launcher-plugin-spell
Architecture: any
Depends:
    aspell,
    ${misc:Depends},
    ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: Spell checking plugin for pop-launcher using aspell as a backend
 This package provides a spell checking plugin for pop-launcher using aspell.
 Searches for the closest matching spelling and copies it to your clipboard.
 .
 Usage:
 In pop launcher type spell followed by your query to search for the closest
 matching spelling. Pressing enter copies the result into the clipboard.